OL,3,CAlmost half of Blue Islands' flights
OL,4,Cdelayed in second quarter of 2025
OL,6,FOnly 55% of Blue Islands' flights were
OL,7,Fon time in the second quarter of this
OL,8,Fyear, according to a new report.
OL,10,FA review by the Civil Aviation
OL,11,FAuthority (CAA) covers the punctuality
OL,12,Fof the 20 largest airlines flying in
OL,13,Fand out of the UK's 25 busiest
OL,14,Fairports.
OL,16,FIt places Jersey's airline at the
OL,17,Fbottom of that list, with the fewest
OL,18,Fflights arriving or departing within
OL,19,F15 minutes of their scheduled time.
