OL,6,FThe CAA calculates delays according to
OL,7,Fthe total minutes all flights were
OL,8,Frecorded late, divided by the total
OL,9,Fnumber of flights operated.
OL,11,FTheir data also shows that Blue
OL,12,FIslands' delays are typically longer
OL,13,Fthan average, and that the airline
OL,14,Fcancelled more flights than any other.
