OL,3,CAlmost half of Blue Islands' flights
OL,4,Cdelayed in second quarter of 2025
OL,6,FIt comes after a report by the
OL,7,Fisland's Comptroller and Auditor
OL,8,FGeneral last week found that, whilst
OL,9,Fthe service provided by Blue Islands
OL,10,Fis critical to the island's
OL,11,Fresilience, further "action is needed
OL,12,Fto enhance the monitoring of critical
OL,13,Ftransport links".
OL,15,FIt also concluded that "reliance on
OL,16,FBlue Islands' small fleet of five
OL,17,Faircraft presents an inherent risk to
OL,18,Fresilience".
