OL,3,CAlmost half of Blue Islands' flights
OL,4,Cdelayed in second quarter of 2025
OL,6,FA Blue Islands spokesperson has
OL,7,Facknowledged that the period covered
OL,8,Fby this report, April to June, was a
OL,9,Fdifficult time for the airline.
OL,11,F"Operational issues - industry-wide
OL,12,Fsupply chain issues and late delivery
OL,13,Fof aircraft - had seriously impacted
OL,14,Four on-time performance in Q2", they
OL,15,Fsay.
OL,17,FMay also saw an emergency landing in
OL,18,FBirmingham that caused further travel
OL,19,Fdisruption.
