OL,3,CAlmost half of Blue Islands' flights
OL,4,Cdelayed in second quarter of 2025
OL,6,F"Since that time, we're heartened to
OL,7,Freport a marked improvement which will
OL,8,Fbe visible in the next set of CAA
OL,9,Ffigures," the spokesperson adds.
OL,11,F"For example, in August, of our 863
OL,12,Fflights, 74% arrived on time and 99%
OL,13,Foperated.
OL,15,F"With our fleet now restored to full
OL,16,Fstrength, we have the resilience to
OL,17,Fdeliver the high levels of operational
OL,18,Fperformance our customers rightly
OL,19,Fexpect."
